reviewText: I love Christy's DVD's!!  She has the very best talent.  I got this for my kids and they really got into it and love that they can be cool on the dance floor!  Thanks Christy - again!

What a waste of money! This is definitely "basic". The moves and the dancers suck. If you can find it under $5, maybe give it a look if your trying to choreograph a small group beginner dance. Otherwise, you could probably get way more for your money elsewhere.
